🚀 Prerequisites
Before running the app, please ensure you have the following:

Expo Go installed on your mobile phone or emulator.

🔧 Setup

1. Install Dependencies
   Download the nessessary dependencies.

2. Configure Firebase
   Conncet you your own firebase conncetion - note that the file in this code is called firebaseConfig

3. Firestore Database
   The app uses a Firestore collection called "User" to store user data. Ensure that the collection is set up correctly in your Firebase project.

📍 Features
The App allows users to make a note book with a map that shows them where the event is located.
Users can click the marker and edit the information linked to the event.
